4
00:00:01,014 --> 00:00:03,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Follow the traffic rules and drive safely."</b></font>

5
00:00:14,454 --> 00:00:17,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Get ready, yo! Now we blow up the horn</i></b></font>

6
00:00:30,744 --> 00:00:34,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>In the silver smoke amidst the frozen city</i></b></font>

7
00:00:34,474 --> 00:00:38,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Payback for a dream I've seen so many times</i></b></font>

8
00:00:38,144 --> 00:00:41,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My body is frozen in a</i>
<i>memory that I can't shake</i></b></font>

9
00:00:41,814 --> 00:00:45,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Slam on the accelerator and deceive myself</i></b></font>

10
00:00:45,584 --> 00:00:48,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Broken in the night</i></b></font>

11
00:00:48,724 --> 00:00:52,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My eyes become sharper</i></b></font>

12
00:00:52,924 --> 00:00:56,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>All from someone's whim</i></b></font>

13
00:00:56,064 --> 00:01:00,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It seems like the world will end any minute</i></b></font>

14
00:01:00,304 --> 00:01:02,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Break into the night, it's the time</i></b></font>

15
00:01:02,174 --> 00:01:05,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>With scared eyes, I'm lost in the night</i></b></font>

16
00:01:05,844 --> 00:01:09,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Embraced by a falling dream</i></b></font>

17
00:01:09,474 --> 00:01:13,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Scared of being alone, missin' my heart</i></b></font>

18
00:01:13,114 --> 00:01:16,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even hurting myself</i></b></font>

19
00:01:16,924 --> 00:01:20,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Love me so much,</i>
<i>enough that I could fall apart</i></b></font>

20
00:01:20,624 --> 00:01:24,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If only I could throw everything away</i></b></font>

21
00:01:24,264 --> 00:01:27,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And just love you</i></b></font>

22
00:01:27,934 --> 00:01:32,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Then I know I could face the truth</i></b></font>

23
00:01:38,144 --> 00:01:42,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, you don't look too sharp.</b></font>

24
00:01:42,014 --> 00:01:45,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you sure you'll be okay in the rain?</b></font>

25
00:01:45,514 --> 00:01:47,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who knows?</b></font>

26
00:01:47,014 --> 00:01:51,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't go too fast in the rain,
so I'll drive normally.</b></font>

27
00:01:51,854 --> 00:01:55,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who knows if I'll be fast or slow?</b></font>

28
00:01:55,354 --> 00:01:57,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll take it easy,</b></font>

29
00:01:57,624 --> 00:02:01,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>'cause if I crashed, my dad would kill me.</b></font>

30
00:02:04,904 --> 00:02:06,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll count down!</b></font>

31
00:02:06,904 --> 00:02:08,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five... Four...</b></font>

32
00:02:08,904 --> 00:02:11,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Three... Two...</b></font>

33
00:02:11,074 --> 00:02:13,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One... Go!</b></font>

34
00:02:14,214 --> 00:02:19,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 23: The Rainy Downhill"</b></font>

35
00:02:25,324 --> 00:02:27,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The S14 got off to a faster start.</b></font>

36
00:02:27,394 --> 00:02:30,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not a turbo, but it has a two-liter engine.</b></font>

37
00:02:30,424 --> 00:02:33,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not just the size of the engine.</b></font>

38
00:02:33,064 --> 00:02:36,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He used the clutch well on the wet surface.</b></font>

39
00:02:36,064 --> 00:02:39,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No wonder he's confident.</b></font>

40
00:02:39,204 --> 00:02:43,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That wasn't the Eight-Six's best start.</b></font>

41
00:02:43,274 --> 00:02:47,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He knows he can catch up once he gets going.</b></font>

42
00:02:49,374 --> 00:02:51,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He took the lead!</i></b></font>

43
00:02:51,344 --> 00:02:54,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Oh, no! His powerful S14 will widen the gap,</i></b></font>

44
00:02:54,454 --> 00:02:56,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>and we'll be left behind!</i></b></font>

45
00:03:09,134 --> 00:03:10,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's way behind.</b></font>

46
00:03:10,634 --> 00:03:13,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This hill is too much for an Eight-Six.</b></font>

47
00:03:13,064 --> 00:03:17,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But it's downhill from here to the finish line.</b></font>

48
00:03:17,274 --> 00:03:21,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That Eight-Six is known for
his killer downhill technique,</b></font>

49
00:03:17,374 --> 00:03:23,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Sekimon Entrance"</b></font>

50
00:03:21,374 --> 00:03:23,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so he'll make a comeback.</b></font>

51
00:03:43,064 --> 00:03:44,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello?</b></font>

52
00:03:44,234 --> 00:03:46,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, big brother.</b></font>

53
00:03:47,404 --> 00:03:50,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six and Kenta in the rain?</b></font>

54
00:03:50,504 --> 00:03:52,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

55
00:03:52,344 --> 00:03:56,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kenta is very confident
racing against the Eight-Six,</b></font>

56
00:03:56,914 --> 00:03:59,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I know it won't be that easy.</b></font>

57
00:03:59,844 --> 00:04:04,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I agree. Drifting through corners at low speed</b></font>

58
00:04:04,484 --> 00:04:08,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is completely different from an actual race.</b></font>

59
00:04:08,354 --> 00:04:13,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. It gets very difficult when
you have to floor the gas pedal.</b></font>

60
00:04:13,264 --> 00:04:16,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What tire grip can
compensate for on a dry surface</b></font>

61
00:04:16,764 --> 00:04:19,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is severely limited in the rain.</b></font>

62
00:04:19,934 --> 00:04:24,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You have to shift the weight properly,</b></font>

63
00:04:24,444 --> 00:04:27,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>or you'll lose control and crash in no time.</b></font>

64
00:04:27,944 --> 00:04:30,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if those two really understand</b></font>

65
00:04:30,814 --> 00:04:34,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the difficulty of a rainy race?</b></font>

66
00:04:34,554 --> 00:04:36,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Interesting...</b></font>

67
00:04:37,554 --> 00:04:39,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Those two..."</b></font>

68
00:04:39,224 --> 00:04:40,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You liar!</b></font>

69
00:04:40,994 --> 00:04:45,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're only interested in the Eight-Six.</b></font>

70
00:05:10,354 --> 00:05:15,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Help! I'm not ready to die!</b></font>

71
00:05:20,264 --> 00:05:24,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Darn... it's coming down harder now.</b></font>

72
00:05:24,104 --> 00:05:26,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The opponent is from Akagi,</b></font>

73
00:05:26,434 --> 00:05:30,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so neither one has the advantage here.</b></font>

74
00:05:30,674 --> 00:05:32,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The problem is the rain.</b></font>

75
00:05:32,604 --> 00:05:36,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if he can perform in the rain?</b></font>

76
00:05:44,254 --> 00:05:46,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure he can,</b></font>

77
00:05:46,584 --> 00:05:50,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>because he makes deliveries every day.</b></font>

78
00:05:50,254 --> 00:05:52,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure he's driven on rainy days.</b></font>

79
00:05:52,364 --> 00:05:54,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course he has!</b></font>

80
00:05:54,764 --> 00:05:57,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then his technique</b></font>

81
00:05:57,934 --> 00:06:00,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>should be effective in the rain, too.</b></font>

82
00:06:07,574 --> 00:06:09,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I won't let you catch up!</i></b></font>

83
00:06:09,744 --> 00:06:12,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll widen the gap.</i></b></font>

84
00:06:12,414 --> 00:06:16,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>In the rain, I can even</i>
<i>outrace turbo-charged cars.</i></b></font>

85
00:06:22,654 --> 00:06:24,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He swung his tail!</b></font>

86
00:06:32,504 --> 00:06:35,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The S14 is running well in the rain.</b></font>

87
00:06:35,274 --> 00:06:38,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's hard to control an FR in the rain.</b></font>

88
00:06:38,344 --> 00:06:42,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. It only spins to the side, not forward.</b></font>

89
00:06:52,924 --> 00:06:54,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's the Eight-Six!</b></font>

90
00:07:02,264 --> 00:07:03,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unbelievable!</b></font>

91
00:07:03,534 --> 00:07:06,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a drift in the rain!</b></font>

92
00:07:15,274 --> 00:07:17,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What was that?</b></font>

93
00:07:17,484 --> 00:07:19,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That drift was scary.</b></font>

94
00:07:19,644 --> 00:07:22,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have goose bumps.</b></font>

95
00:07:27,294 --> 00:07:31,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Is this the same person</i>
<i>who was lost in a daydream?</i></b></font>

96
00:07:33,564 --> 00:07:37,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He said he would take it easy...</i></b></font>

97
00:07:37,204 --> 00:07:41,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So is this how he normally drives?!</i></b></font>

98
00:07:41,004 --> 00:07:44,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Besides, it's impossible to see in this rain.</i></b></font>

99
00:07:44,344 --> 00:07:46,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>How does he do it?</i></b></font>

100
00:07:46,204 --> 00:07:51,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's so dark that I can't even see the road!</i></b></font>

101
00:07:57,424 --> 00:07:59,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Stop that ringing!</i></b></font>

102
00:07:59,254 --> 00:08:02,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This speed is insane!</i></b></font>

103
00:08:17,244 --> 00:08:20,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's not human.</i></b></font>

104
00:08:20,244 --> 00:08:22,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's a monster!</i></b></font>

105
00:08:45,364 --> 00:08:46,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm on!</i></b></font>

106
00:08:46,864 --> 00:08:50,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm in top form tonight!</i></b></font>

107
00:08:50,544 --> 00:08:54,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll put an end to the</i>
<i>Eight-Six's undefeated streak!</i></b></font>

108
00:08:54,074 --> 00:08:57,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's not Keisuke or Ryosuke,</i></b></font>

109
00:08:57,744 --> 00:09:00,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but me who will defeat him!</i></b></font>

110
00:09:01,614 --> 00:09:03,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What?!</i></b></font>

111
00:09:11,064 --> 00:09:13,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Eight-Six is on my tail.</i></b></font>

112
00:09:13,964 --> 00:09:17,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>How? It can't be!</i></b></font>

113
00:09:17,464 --> 00:09:19,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What's happening?</i></b></font>

114
00:09:19,734 --> 00:09:25,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We haven't gone through</i>
<i>that many downhill corners yet.</i></b></font>

115
00:09:25,174 --> 00:09:27,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This isn't happening!</i></b></font>

116
00:09:27,844 --> 00:09:31,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I got caught so easily...</i></b></font>

117
00:09:31,184 --> 00:09:34,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...going downhill in the rain.</i></b></font>

118
00:09:36,984 --> 00:09:38,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But...</b></font>

119
00:09:38,784 --> 00:09:40,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...it's not over yet!</b></font>

120
00:10:13,124 --> 00:10:15,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're only inches apart!</b></font>

121
00:10:35,874 --> 00:10:38,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Look! The Eight-Six is cutting in!</b></font>

122
00:10:58,364 --> 00:11:00,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is passing him!</b></font>

123
00:11:19,224 --> 00:11:21,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He made it look easy.</b></font>

124
00:11:21,054 --> 00:11:22,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you kidding?</b></font>

125
00:11:22,894 --> 00:11:25,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was worth waiting in the rain.</b></font>

126
00:11:25,564 --> 00:11:27,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

127
00:11:29,534 --> 00:11:31,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't keep up!</i></b></font>

128
00:11:31,204 --> 00:11:34,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The gap widens with each corner!</i></b></font>

129
00:11:39,704 --> 00:11:42,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't go around the corners as fast.</i></b></font>

130
00:11:42,044 --> 00:11:45,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What could be making the difference?</i></b></font>

131
00:11:45,384 --> 00:11:48,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I thought the rain was on my side!</i></b></font>

132
00:12:03,094 --> 00:12:05,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right, I see.</b></font>

133
00:12:12,304 --> 00:12:14,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Word from the mid-point.</b></font>

134
00:12:14,844 --> 00:12:18,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six passed your guy.</b></font>

135
00:12:18,184 --> 00:12:22,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess he was way out of Kenta's league.</b></font>

136
00:12:22,354 --> 00:12:26,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He did well, though.</b></font>

137
00:12:26,424 --> 00:12:29,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is even fast in the rain.</b></font>

138
00:12:31,424 --> 00:12:34,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was obvious even before the race.</b></font>

139
00:12:34,094 --> 00:12:38,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The weather plays no part
in defeating the Eight-Six.</b></font>

140
00:12:41,874 --> 00:12:45,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's finally your brother's turn.</b></font>

141
00:13:14,534 --> 00:13:16,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Welcome!
--Welcome!</b></font>

142
00:13:17,844 --> 00:13:20,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Welcome.</b></font>

143
00:13:20,474 --> 00:13:21,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway...</b></font>

144
00:13:21,814 --> 00:13:25,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...we now know that he can
race just as well in the rain.</b></font>

145
00:13:25,714 --> 00:13:29,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's becoming more like
a true racer every day.</b></font>

146
00:13:29,214 --> 00:13:33,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He willingly took the S14's
challenge last night.</b></font>

147
00:13:33,024 --> 00:13:36,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His daydreaming seems to have passed.</b></font>

148
00:13:36,194 --> 00:13:39,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think our operation was a big success.</b></font>

149
00:13:39,824 --> 00:13:41,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

150
00:13:42,534 --> 00:13:46,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyhow, Itsuki, you were lucky</b></font>

151
00:13:46,904 --> 00:13:51,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to be able to experience
that rainy downhill battle.</b></font>

152
00:13:51,544 --> 00:13:56,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was so scary that I
thought I would die for sure!</b></font>

153
00:13:56,544 --> 00:14:00,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Besides, he told me to sit in the back instead.</b></font>

154
00:14:01,714 --> 00:14:03,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In the back?</b></font>

155
00:14:04,854 --> 00:14:06,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Why?
--No idea.</b></font>

156
