171
00:14:59,744 --> 00:15:02,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much.</b></font>

172
00:15:02,344 --> 00:15:06,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have no idea how much better he'll get.</i></b></font>

173
00:15:06,014 --> 00:15:07,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

174
00:15:14,924 --> 00:15:16,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who is she?</b></font>

175
00:15:16,094 --> 00:15:17,424
