<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Trouble!</b></font>

187
00:16:29,034 --> 00:16:32,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He may start daydreaming about her again!</b></font>

188
00:16:32,534 --> 00:16:34,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do something, Itsuki.</b></font>

189
00:16:34,034 --> 00:16:38,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There aren't any more races for him to see!</b></font>

190
00:16:38,174 --> 00:16:41,874
