192
00:16:44,044 --> 00:16:45,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know that!</b></font>

193
00:16:45,914 --> 00:16:47,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi!</b></font>

194
00:16:47,854 --> 00:16:50,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go to Akina for a spin tonight!</b></font>

195
