196
00:17:07,234 --> 00:17:10,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess it's because of last night.</b></font>

197
00:18:09,864 --> 00:18:11,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello?</b></font>

198
00:18:11,364 --> 00:18:13,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who is this?</b></font>

199
00:18:13,534 --> 00:18:16,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's me. It's been a while, Bunta.</b></font>

200
00:18:16,674 --> 00:18:18,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, it's you.</b></font>

201
00:18:18,804 --> 00:18:20,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's the occasion?</b></font>

202
00:18:20,304 --> 00:18:22,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did you crash and get hospitalized?</b></font>

203
00:18:22,474 --> 00:18:24,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You wish.</b></font>

204
00:18:24,314 --> 00:18:26,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By the way...</b></font>

205
00:18:26,144 --> 00:18:29,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I hear people are talking about your son.</b></font>

206
00:18:29,814 --> 00:18:31,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hear he's good.</b></font>

207
00:18:33,854 --> 00:18:36,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? This Saturday?</b></font>

208
00:18:36,494 --> 00:18:39,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Against Ryosuke Takahashi? Who is that?</b></font>

209
00:18:39,324 --> 00:18:40,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't know him?</b></font>

210
00:18:40,994 --> 00:18:44,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even my people know who he is.</b></font>

211
00:18:44,564 --> 00:18:48,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hear he's the best street racer in Gunma.</b></font>

212
00:18:48,074 --> 00:18:52,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My son and he are racing, huh?</b></font>

213
00:18:52,044 --> 00:18:55,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who do you think will win?</b></font>

214
00:18:55,044 --> 00:18:59,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who knows? We'll find out this Saturday.</b></font>

215
00:19:01,214 --> 00:19:03,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You haven't changed a bit.</b></font>

216
00:19:03,514 --> 00:19:08,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm curious about the drift
your son learned from you.</b></font>

217
00:19:14,894 --> 00:19:19,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You scarred me for life
