218
00:19:19,564 --> 00:19:21,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That was years ago.</b></font>

219
00:19:21,064 --> 00:19:24,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Mr. Tsuchiya, we need you.
