221
00:20:13,824 --> 00:20:17,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can tell that you've improved a lot, Itsuki.</b></font>

222
00:20:17,724 --> 00:20:20,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You really think so?</b></font>

223
00:20:20,824 --> 00:20:24,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That means a lot coming from you, Takumi!</b></font>

224
00:20:24,494 --> 00:20:28,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been practicing the "grip run," you know?</b></font>

225
00:20:31,274 --> 00:20:34,444
