227
00:20:37,774 --> 00:20:40,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Illusionary Hell and Tear!"</b></font>

228
00:20:45,184 --> 00:20:47,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is strange!</b></font>

229
00:20:47,754 --> 00:20:50,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I had no problem with it yesterday.</b></font>

230
00:20:50,524 --> 00:20:52,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The next corner, then!</b></font>

231
00:20:56,034 --> 00:20:58,864
