232
00:20:58,864 --> 00:21:00,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hold on, Itsuki!</b></font>

233
00:21:09,874 --> 00:21:11,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can relax now.</b></font>

234
00:21:11,384 --> 00:21:15,684
