241
00:21:36,404 --> 00:21:39,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you get what I'm saying?</b></font>

242
00:21:39,244 --> 00:21:41,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No idea.</b></font>

243
00:21:41,644 --> 00:21:43,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's all a riddle to me.</b></font>

244
00:21:43,474 --> 00:21:46,044
